dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.swcomponenttemplate.swcinternalbehavior.perinstancememory

Interface IPerInstanceMemory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable

    public interface IPerInstanceMemory
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IPerInstanceMemory: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Defines a memory-block that needs to be available for each instance of the SW-component. This is typically only useful if supportsMultipleInstantiation is TRUE of if the component defines NVRAM access via permanent blocks.
